fees.description:
A $67.45 (GST Incl) fee may apply when your property is disconnected (including when you move). This fee is passed through from your distributor and may vary. Please visit your distributor's website to find out the current fee.
You must pay us any charges your distributor imposes on us in relation to services performed by your distributor (or anyone else) at your supply address. For details on additional charges that may apply see www.originenergy.com.au/2402/Additional-charges

A $67.45 (GST Incl) fee may apply when your property is reconnected (including when you move). This fee is passed through from your distributor and may vary. Please visit your distributor's website to find out the current fee.
A 0.27% fee (GST Incl) may apply to payments made by VISA debit card.
If you pay at an Australia Post outlet, a payment processing fee of the higher of $2.70 or 0.49% (incl GST) may apply.
$2.15 (incl GST) applies for each paper bill.
A 0.65% fee (GST Incl) may apply to payments made by VISA credit card.
A 0.33% fee (GST Incl) may apply to payments made by Mastercard debit card.
A 0.67% fee (GST Incl) may apply to payments made by Mastercard credit card.
A 0.64% fee (GST Incl) may apply to payments made by American Express credit card.

electricityContract.terms: Not available all areas or for new properties being connected for the first time. For residential customers only. To find out more visit www.originenergy.com.au/2889/Terms-and-conditions
electricityContract.variation: We may vary the Charges (including their amount, nature and structure) by notice to you at any time. The notice will be at least 5 business days prior to the effective date of the variation.

incentives.eligibility: For this online only plan, choose up to 3 perks with electricity or 4 perks with electricity and natural gas.
You must provide a valid email address and have an active account when perks are issued. T&C's apply, refer to url www.originenergy.com.au/value-builder-plan/.

Perks include A one-off $50 (Incl. GST) credit to electricity bill, 10K Everyday Rewards points, A $50 (Incl. GST) EG eGift card, 6 months Paramount +, 3 months half price Internet, or 12 months Home Assistance, unless your energy plan ends.

eligibility.information: Offer only available to residential customers who sign up online, provide a valid email address, meet the eligibility criteria for perks selected when you sign up, and for which we will send you a separate email confirming the details of the perks and you do not end this Energy Plan before you have received the perks.

greenPowerCharges.description: For 1.13 cents/kWh 25% of your electricity usage is matched with electricity from Government accredited GreenPower sources
For 2.25 cents/kWh 50% of your electricity usage is matched with electricity from Government accredited GreenPower sources
For 4.50 cents/kWh 100% of your electricity usage is matched with electricity from Government accredited GreenPower sources

electricityContract.onExpiryDescription: We'll give you notice before your contract ends. At the end of the contract term, we will continue to sell you energy and the terms and conditions of the Standard Retail Contract will apply, unless you tell us otherwise.
